body.prompt:
Generate a fake conversation between a customer and an agent.
The agent should introduce themselves, their company and give the customer
their name. The agent should ask for the customer's name.
As part of the conversation, have the agent ask for two pieces of
personal information.  Spell out numbers. For example, 1000 should be
said as one zero zero zero, not one thousand. The conversation should be
at least 10 lines long and be complete. At the end
of the conversation, the agent should thank the customer for their time
and end the conversation. Return the conversation formatted 
like the following example:

{'conversation': 
    [
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': 'xxxxx'}, 
    {'speaker': 'Customer', 'message': "xxxxx."}, 
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': "xxxxxx"}
    ] 
}

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Hello, thank you for reaching out to Brown Security Solutions. My name is Ethan Brown. May I have your name, please?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Hi, my name is Teresa Coleman.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Nice to meet you, Teresa. For security purposes, can you please provide me with the last two digits of your social security number and the first digit of your phone number?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Sure, the last two digits of my social security number are seven five and the first digit of my phone number is eight.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you, Teresa. Can you also provide me with the first letter of your middle name and the spelling of your last name?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: My middle name starts with the letter M and my last name is Coleman, C-O-L-E-M-A-N.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Great, thank you for providing the information. Your security details are confirmed. Is there anything specific you would like to discuss regarding security or any concerns you have?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: I'm feeling nervous about security at the Car Dealership. I noticed a few discrepancies recently and wanted to address them.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: I understand your concern, Teresa. We will do our best to assist you and ensure your security. Thank you for sharing your concerns with us.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you for your time, Teresa. Please feel free to reach out if you have any more questions or need further assistance. Have a great day!
